How It Works
We’re here to help you find small business funding for up to $350,000. That’s why we’ve set up a network of reputable small business funding providers. Just fill out our short, hassle-free form and we’ll try to pair you with one of the providers we work with. You can get started by clicking on the button below.
Start Now













Step One:Fill Out Our Form
Our secure funding request form gathers all of the information we need to find you a provider. The form is easy to fill out and it uses the latest data-encryption technology, so your information should be safe.













Step Two:Get Paired
After you submit the form, we’ll try to find you a funding provider. Our network is packed with reputable providers. Our large and diverse network means you have a chance of being paired with a provider for your business.













Step Three:Work with the Provider
Our job is done after we find you a funding provider. They will guide you through the process of obtaining financing for your business. Please note that we are not a provider. We will not offer you an application or a funding agreement. Don’t worry – you’ll be in good hands. We only work with the most respectable providers.








Why Lendza.com?
Everyone in the Lendza family is a well-seasoned member of the financial industry. We know what it takes to build a strong network of providers. We work around the clock to form strong relationships with our providers. We’re also proactive with our technology. We are always adjusting our routing system to figure out new and better ways to find you funding. Our goal is to pair every potential borrower with a funding source. We’re sure you’ll enjoy working with us.



fill out our form
To get started, simply fill outour online funding request form.







We only work with respectable providers.










































Lendza.com – Small Business Financing Products | Learn More



































