PREFERRED REWARDS





 See preferred rewards details for Cash Rewards. Link opens a pop up window

Preferred Rewards
Preferred Rewards gives you benefits and rewards across your eligible Bank of America® banking and Merrill Edge® investment accounts. When you are enrolled in the program, you will increase your BankAmericard Cash Rewards™ 10% customer bonus to a 25% - 75% rewards bonus every time you redeem your cash rewards directly into your Bank of America® checking or savings account.
To learn more about this program call 1.888.888.7937.










 See preferred rewards details for Travel Rewards. Link opens a pop up window

Preferred Rewards
Preferred Rewards gives you benefits and rewards across your eligible Bank of America® banking and Merrill Edge® investment accounts. When you are enrolled in the program, you will increase your BankAmericard Travel Rewards® 10% customer points bonus to a 25%-75% rewards bonus on every purchase.
To learn more about this program call
1.888.888.7937.













